{"tid":1399793,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(幫推) 你班保安員下年新年係咪唔想收利是？","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:21:07.000Z","uid":160887,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d62f7ed398a6194b39fea6634dfcdfc45ee0a267","tid":1399793,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"我話知你係藍定黃絲<br />\n你地責任就係保護住客安全<br />\n<br />\n見你地個個燕瘦環肥，骨格精奇<br />\n我都唔預你班人會幫手捉賊，頂門<br />\n但你地可唔可以盡返你嘅責任<br />\n見到陌生人就咪撚開門<br />\n仲要成班蒙哂面拎住槍既<br />\n動動腦，轉轉彎啦<br />\n<br />\n你地平時返夜班有幾多人會偷懶瞓覺<br />\n我哋已經隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n而家呢啲大是大非嘅時候你就同我玩啲咁嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n你哋仲係咁鍾意同d警察合作<br />\n下年唔使旨意諗住下會俾幾多利是你<br />\n平時新年就識笑笑口企出泥，余生前余生後咁<br />\n話知你下年幾多人其左個大堂馺熟狗頭咁款<br />\n我一個仙都唔會比<br />\n<br />\n係到同全港保安員講明<br />\n你地唔做好本份，下年好自為之<br />\n蛇齋餅糭就有你份，利是就咪撚諗<br />\n<br />\n[red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span>[/red"},{"pid":"ad2e0a51fa35283f5581e8ed2512b4dcc86306a5","tid":1399793,"uid":160887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGvLCym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGvLCym.png&h=ef7b1189&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b0fc587e14269ed8659a2ef8c3e24ce074275e5","tid":1399793,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edef29319061bb1339b0caceb709dc220198f58c","tid":1399793,"uid":160887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b0fc587e14269ed8659a2ef8c3e24ce074275e5","tid":1399793,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"只要有一個保安再玩野<br />\n全港保安下年受把啦"},{"pid":"94b5ea28d9d41002e07ed4f46825fc9563433659","tid":1399793,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"